article_id:1862,category_name:News,title_name:New Year's Party Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/72108ddbf50804b9194bc21dbc5920cb.png,message:<div>New Year&#39;s Party Packs are available under Value Packs in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/72108ddbf50804b9194bc21dbc5920cb.png"></div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609739940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Check out the details of each pack below.</div><div><br></div><div>■New Year&#39;s Party Pack: Quad Sunlight Stone Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading dragons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Sunlight Stone &times; 4</div><div><br></div><div>■New Year&#39;s Party Pack: Adventurer Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading adventurers and unlocking mana nodes.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 10</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament &times; 10</div><div>・Gold Crystal &times; 1,000</div><div>・Mana &times; 1,000,000</div><div><br></div><div>■New Year&#39;s Party Pack: Superior Orb Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for unlocking mana circles.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 4</div><div>・Incandescence Orb &times; 50</div><div>・Tsunami Orb &times; 50</div><div>・Tempest Orb &times; 50</div><div>・Resplendence Orb &times; 50</div><div>・Abaddon Orb &times; 50</div><div>・Rainbow Orb &times; 50</div><div><br></div><div>■New Year&#39;s Party Pack: 6★ Weapon Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading 6★ weapons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Adamantite Ingot &times; 1</div><div>・Twinkling Sand &times; 5</div><div>・Orichalcum &times; 5</div><div><br></div><div>■New Year&#39;s Party Pack: Diamantium Special</div><div>This pack contains a large amount of diamantium.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・1,200 (840 + 360 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For information about each pack, select the Shop on the Home page, then select New Year&#39;s Party Packs.</div><div>2. The New Year&#39;s Party Pack: Superior Orb Special and New Year&#39;s Party Pack: 6★ Weapon Upgrade Special may be purchased twice during the availability period and the other New Year&#39;s Party Packs may be purchased once during the availability period.</div><div>3. Certain New Year&#39;s Party Packs are not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1609394400,update_time1608520384